        <!-- The Overview -->
        <section class="mb-16 fade-section">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 border-b border-ide-border pb-2">The Overview</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-ide-text-muted leading-relaxed">
                <p>Chirp is a comprehensive enterprise-grade messaging solution designed to demonstrate mastery over modern cross-platform development. Built entirely in Kotlin, it leverages Kotlin Multiplatform (KMP) for shared state management and Compose Multiplatform (CMP) for unified UI rendering across mobile and desktop platforms.</p>
            </div>
