                <li><strong>100% Code Sharing</strong> achieved for business logic across Android, iOS, and Desktop platforms using KMP.</li>
                <li><strong>Zero-polling communication</strong> integrated via WebSockets, drastically reducing backend payload overhead and latency.</li>
                <li><strong>Flawless offline capabilities</strong> enabling continuous data interaction and background sync queued implicitly upon reconnection.</li>
            </ul>
